{"tid":1411983,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"講真，民間記者會可唔可以搵100毛搞？","createTime":"2019-08-05T05:03:56.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-05T05:13:20.000Z","uid":61589,"like":7,"dislike":28,"uniUserReply":9,"replies":[{"pid":"5e0deefec1485dcc7340425cc11be03799a6fa62","tid":1411983,"uid":61589,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-05T05:03:56.000Z","msg":"我諗左一陣，100毛<br />\n應該係最有人力物力同經驗搞呢壇野既人<br />\n<br />\n首先背景，成個機構黃底呢樣嘢大家都知喇<br />\n佢地都係玩時事惡搞起家<br />\n要林日曦支持應該唔難<br />\n<br />\n講人力物力同知名度，佢地本身係上巿既網上媒體公司<br />\n都造就左一班後生仔認得既KOL<br />\n呢樣嘢更加無容置議<br />\n<br />\n講經驗，佢地一樣大把<br />\n惡搞過一堆CCTVB同港台節目<br />\n<br />\n有無係100毛既巴絲可以提議下？"},{"pid":"468ec9059276145a1f203566702b182ed89c6717","tid":1411983,"uid":61831,"like":6,"dislike":0,"score":6,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-05T05:07:53.000Z","msg":"咁咪即係推100毛出黎做靶"},{"pid":"0aa959b71d27077867e55808f2cc0bc2fcb49ef2","tid":1411983,"uid":38518,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-05T05:08:20.000Z","msg":"無大台"},{"pid":"b55f886deff77f67f3036442a027349733256800","tid":1411983,"uid":48143,"like":10,"dislike":1,"score":9,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-05T05:08:27.000Z","msg":"比佢地好易膠化"},{"pid":"16b8c42337dc791b365418c4c293ae1ea87c43c2","tid":1411983,"uid":54678,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-05T05:08:37.000Z","msg":"我驚膠化成件事 雖然佢地好多人睇"},{"pid":"ee415a93dfb5fbd8b43026ae13c3ee480efa398b","tid":1411983,"uid":32051,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-05T05:09:45.000Z","msg":"100毛間嘢d人黃<br />\n<br />\n但公司個底係紅<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n你投放咁多資源，最後可能會變成中共既武器<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n由佢繼續啦<br />\n咪做多左"},{"pid":"c96c395f9e61319b22b5fc0ee4f387b532f052e4","tid":1411983,"uid":61589,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"468ec9059276145a1f203566702b182ed89c6717","tid":1411983,"uid":61831,"like":6,"dislike":0,"score":6,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-05T05:07:53.000Z","msg":"咁咪即係推100毛出黎做靶"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-05T05:10:11.00